dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Santa Rita Peak quadrangle, Fresno and San Benito counties, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Santa Rita Peak CA 1969. Photorevised 1984. DMA 1856 I SE - series V895."
"Edwin B. Eckel and W.B. Myers honorary map."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology, most recent 1969.
